{"tid":42643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"37歲女Apps識朋友 被騙近27萬財物","createTime":"2016-12-17T00:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T04:18:28.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e35c766d285d286ed947062f12a66448cedfc1a","tid":42643,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:08:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>37歲女Apps識朋友 被騙近27萬財物</strong><br />\n<br />\n2016-12-17 07:16:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n一名37歲姓韋女子，凌晨約1時到九龍城警署報案，據報她較早前透過手機應用程式認識一名男子，該名男子要求她送贈一部手提電腦及手提電話，共約港幣1.7萬元。<br />\n<br />\n女事主按該名男子指示把物件寄至一個外地地址。其後，她再按該名男子指示先後五次將共約25萬港元轉賬至5個外地戶口。她懷疑受騙遂報案。案件由九龍城警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"124706586fd3953f89ac7e88643c7b9b47c97355","tid":42643,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:11:03.000Z","msg":"37歲(交友)"},{"pid":"038adc499dd0d18d364400ce42b3c88d778b9bc8","tid":42643,"uid":127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:24:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>37歲(交友)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49865379cb0fe444cd988b8f733c45555acf74e","tid":42643,"uid":42575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:24:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>37歲(交友)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f927bb66617075dd7047d0de05e3ec21ce528ce","tid":42643,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:25:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>37歲(交友)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你地個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f711726bf0ab7c30712065a157246e91a70782d","tid":42643,"uid":28153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB